dilation parameters\nwithout significant degradation in accuracy, provided the cross-correlation\nfunction is accurately known.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 9 Aug 2022 19:09:15 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 19 Sep 2022 16:20:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-09-20"}
