ich is almost 8 times\nsmaller than required for that model. The proposed model also sustained its\nperformance under relatively similar unseen acoustic conditions and at\npositions in the vicinity of its training position.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 10 Aug 2022 07:07:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-08-11"}
